感謝您停留在我的網站，代表您認同我的審美觀，也同樣重視自家產品的設計風格。
我在尋找一個能重視功能與美感並存的工作環境。
兼具扎實的設計基礎與多年產品開發經驗，擅長以簡潔、獨特的設計風格，將美學融入產品功能之中。
我深信，兼具實用性與美感的介面設計，不僅能提升使用體驗，還能讓您的產品更加精緻且強大。
期待與您共同打造出色的作品！

Thanks for stopping by my website!
It means that you appreciate my sense of design and care about how your products look and feel.
I’m seeking a workplace that values both functionality and aesthetics.
With a strong design background and years of product design experience, I'm specialize in creating clean, unique designs that blend style with usability.
I believe that when a product works well and looks good, it not only enhances the user experience but also makes the product stand out.
Can’t wait to team up and create something amazing together!
